make a stand when reality itself is shifting and crumbling all around them?<br /><br />At once a relentless pageturner and an intricate science-fiction puzzlebox about time, identity, and memory, Recursion is a thriller as only Blake Crouch could imagine it—and his most ambitious, mind-boggling, irresistible work to date.</span></div></div></div></div><div data-testid="genresList" class="BookPageMetadataSection__genres"><ul class="CollapsableList" aria-label="Top genres for this book"><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genre"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/science-fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Science Fiction</span></a></span> <span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genre"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Fiction</span></a></span> <span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genre"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/thriller" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Thriller</span></a></span> <span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genre"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/time-travel" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Time Travel</span></a></span> <div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium" aria-label="Show all items in the list"><span class="Button__labelItem">...more</span></button></div></ul></div><div class="BookDetails"><div class="CollapsableList"><span class="Text Text__body3"><div class="FeaturedDetails"><p data-testid="pagesFormat">329 pages, Hardcover</p><p data-testid="publicationInfo">First published June 11, 2019</p><p data-testid="awards"><span class="CollapsableList"><span data-testid="award"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/21332-goodreads-choice-award">Goodreads Choice Award</a>, Science Fiction<span class="Text Text__su